title: Me too, like the little, Poseidon or mermaid
content: Will not want to get out !  Because in your lovely balloon, in the warm water of your belly,  I will want forever swim !  But, Premiere Neige, to make the little you exit your womb,  just whisper,  Out in the wild, my big blue lakes are awaiting for you !
contentWithMarkup:
Will not want to get out !

Because in your lovely balloon, in the warm water of your belly,

I will want forever swim !

But, Premiere Neige, to make the little you exit your womb,

just whisper,

Out in the wild, my big blue lakes are awaiting for you !
